{
  "texts": [
    "This collaboration improves overall food safety by enabling stakeholders to share information about risks, best practices, and compliance efforts.",
    "It also facilitates data integration with other technologies, such as AI and IoT, to enhance food safety management.",
    "Smart devices and roboticsSmart devices and robotics are transforming food security by introducing advanced technologies that enhance monitoring, efficiency, and quality control throughout the food supply chain.",
    "Smart devices are increasingly integrated into advanced food processing systems.",
    "For instance, robotic arms equipped with AI and hyperspectral imaging are used to detect microbial contamination during ultrasonic sterilization, ensuring safety and uniformity across batches."
  ]
}